name: Glow of Love Flowers
description:
A radiant smile  can describe many things. Cultivated with generosity and love, it can transpose a situation of happiness and relaxation.

Glow of Love Flowers features a humanoid creature planted in a vase with several edelweiss, a flower whose story is an epic proof of love. Enigmatic snakes surround and protect the humanoid planted, in the background various cultural elements of the island of Florianópolis are attached, generating hilarious and mystical aspects.
